#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "Básicos"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click on the planning to add a new shift"
msgstr "Haz clic en la planificación para agregar un nuevo turno"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Descubre más sobre Odoo con nuestra"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to\n"
"            improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Descubre las funciones básicas de este paquete y explora todas las "
"posibilidades que te ofrece Odoo \n"
"            para mejorar tu experiencia."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do You Want to Go Further?"
msgstr "¿Quieres saber más?"

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Employees can have multiple roles. Those are defined in their employee "
"record."
msgstr ""
"Los empleados pueden tener varias funciones. Defínelas en sus registros."

#. module: thrift_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:thrift_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "¡Hola!"

